The Second Beta of my map. If I do not submit another by the deadline, this will be my final submission. If you find any bugs/glitches, please let me know so I can fix them! As well, if you see anything that you think should change, let me know so I can change it, I'm not psychic. Contains 32 Slots Not yet optimized (weird Areaportal errors present, if you can help me with them, PM me) Contains over 16 custom textures, 6 custom models, HDR Glow lighting, and music within the map!
To activate the music, go into one of the two DJ booths in the lower section of the spawn areas (they are located in the booth next to the dance poles), and press the console with the glowing green light. At the moment, there is no way to stop the music from playing once it's started, only to restart it.

Otstrel.ru presents new gungame map gg_xlighty.

This is our first map. We made it from scratch in 2 weeks. There are two floors, round stairs, house, tunnel, towers, and orange textures. There are some gungame specific hint places, a lot of color lights, and of course grenades! Custom textures and radar minimap included in bsp file.

Map is best played with 8-16 players in both DM and Classic GunGame modes.
Feedbacks are always welcome.

This is an adaptation of the UT2004 Morpheous map for Gungame.
It features low gravity combat between 3 simple buildings high in the air.

Careful - It is fatal to miss a jump where you can't reach the middle platform.

Due to reports of server crashing, I have uploaded a newer version with HDR compile and no NAV.

A gungame map with lots of curved twists and turns.  Includes a sidebar tunnel and some special sniper zones on the walls.  Note that the windows over the sniper zones will indicate if a player is within the sniper tube or platform (as does the sign within the building).  The map utilizes standard textures (although this map could have been a dev texture map...) but has some uncommon shapes and cover.

Inspired by one of my favorite online games (The World's Hardest Game), this map is a replica to level 8/30 from the original game. 

- 28 spawn points
- Custom Radar
- Playable "secret" Theme music (invisible button on back side of red block)
- Optimized for high fps
